name: #NFTARTIST
description:
TOOK MY CLOUT PILLS TODAY! LIKE, RETWEET, FOLLOW, TAG UR FRIENDS! JOIN ME IN SPACES SO I CAN REACH MY ENGAGEMENT TARGETS :)

This is the price we pay to play in the electric renaissance, gas got nothing on the cost of soulless shilling, empty clout chasing tweets and sucking the proverbial dick of the algorithm gods.. It's ok we all do it, unfortunate necessity of an artist in 2021, but fml sometimes I just wanna paint, get high and talk shit with nftfam in spaces.
